import React from 'react'
import './../static/style/components/header.css'
import {
    Row,
    Col,
    Menu,
    Icon
} from 'antd'

const Header = () => {
    return ( <
        div className = "header" >
        <
        Row type = "flex"
        justify = "center" >
        <
        Col > < /Col> <
        Col > < /Col> <
        /Row> <
        /div>
    )
}
export default Header
